    "body" : "<p>If you know how much elements the array has, a simple way is doing this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String appendedString = \"\" + array[0] + \"\" + array[1] + \"\" + array[2] + \"\" + array[3]; \n</code></pre>\n"
