    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>When we use stream we do have more flexibility, like <BR>\nmap --&gt; convert any array object to toString<BR>\nfilter --&gt; remove when it is empty<BR>\njoin --&gt; Adding joining character</p>\n<pre><code>    //Deduplicate the comma character in the input string\n    String[] splits = input.split(&quot;\\\\s*,\\\\s*&quot;);\n    return Arrays.stream(splits).filter(StringUtils::isNotBlank).collect(Collectors.joining(&quot;, &quot;));\n</code></pre>\n"
